status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$X_1,X_2,X_3,X_4$
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 Then, one possible replicate might be 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$X_2,X_2,X_2,X_4$
\end_layout

\end_inset

